        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>St Louis</placeName>
                <date>April 16/54</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I shall remit to<lb/> you by the end of this week my reasons<lb/>
                for writing now is that I have spare time<lb/>
                <sic>wheras</sic> in the week my time is so taken<lb/> up by labor that I avail
                myself of the<lb/> present time, the following persons<lb/> in your list are not in
                the city <persName>S. Keller</persName><lb/>
                <persName>J H Cohen</persName>, <persName>A N Hart</persName> &amp; <persName>W St
                    Johns</persName> of those<lb/> here the following refused to take the bible<lb/>
                <persName>M. Abrahams</persName>. <persName>J Barnum</persName>
                <persName>A Langsdorf</persName>
                <persName>J Woolf</persName><lb/>
                <persName>A L Kumell</persName>. <persName>L H Plahto</persName>
                <persName>J Micathened</persName><lb/> to have them advertised in the Occident<lb/>
                particularly as <persName>H Plahto</persName> gave me an order<lb/> for a set of
                    <persName>Piza</persName> Books according to your<lb/> circular. I Received from
                    <persName>Mr Lats</persName> their<lb/> Tiphillas<add>?</add> 1-250-1-2.75 &amp;
                1,5.000 The 2.75 one<lb/> I sold at $3.00 I also sold the 2.50 one the other is<lb/>
                much <sic>soild</sic> and will never bring the price you<lb/> will please inform me
                    <sic>wether</sic> I shall return<lb/> it to <persName>Mr Lats</persName> a sett
                is for 3.00 as I think<lb/> that is about as much as it will bring<lb/> it may fetch
                50/cents more. I received <persName>Dias</persName> Letters<lb/> through the mail
                also the four Hagodahs which<lb/> came very opportune I shall now give you</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>of my stewardship I sold to private persons<lb/> four copies of the bible 2 a 11.00
                &amp; 2—8.00<lb/> besides several <persName>Dias</persName> Letters I had also
                to<lb/> pay one Sharnas five pr cent on<lb/> one hundred and five dollars the
                persons being<lb/> at a distance than in my neighborhood<lb/> I collect myself a
                shall do it</p>
            <table cols="4" rows="11">
                <row>
                    <cell><persName role="author">H Myers</persName> Dr to <persName>I
                            Leeser</persName></cell>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell><persName role="author">H Myers</persName> Or</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>To <sic>ballance</sic> of Bill—</cell>
                    <cell>50</cell>
                    <cell>Freight &amp;c</cell>
                    <cell>10.50</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>1 Bible <add>?</add></cell>
                    <cell>9—</cell>
                    <cell>5 pr cent 105</cell>
                    <cell>5.25</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>1 Set <persName>Piza</persName> Books</cell>
                    <cell>25—</cell>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>$15.75</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>13 Bibles 8—</cell>
                    <cell>104—</cell>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>165.25</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>1—</cell>
                    <cell>9—</cell>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>8 <persName>Dias</persName>
                        <add>?</add></cell>
                    <cell>6—</cell>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>1 Tephillim</cell>
                    <cell>2 50</cell>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>3—</cell>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>159—</cell>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>2 Bibles 11-00</cell>
                    <cell>18.100.</cell>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
            </table>
            <p>from this $165.25 will be deducted Exchange &amp;<lb/> discount, you will please
                charge<lb/> a <persName>J Lats</persName> with 1 <persName>Dias</persName> letters
                you<lb/> will also send the occident to <persName>J. A Hart</persName><lb/> of this
                city commencing if come with the<lb/> first number just out he his good
                <add>?</add><lb/> I have now on hand 5 Bibles at $800<lb/> 1 at $9.00 2 at $11.00
                &amp; 6 <persName>Dias</persName> Letter's<lb/> you may rely upon my using my<lb/>
                <sic>axertions</sic> to affect sales it <sic>ocurrs</sic> to me</p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p>that it would be a good plan to advertise<lb/> them but the <sic>expence</sic> would
                not <add>?</add><lb/> me in doing so without your consent<lb/> the following Name I
                got to your<lb/> prayer Books according to the<lb/> German &amp; Polish Jews</p>
            <table cols="4" rows="4">
                <row>
                    <cell>
                        <persName>R Kiche</persName>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>2 copies</cell>
                    <cell>
                        <persName>L M Prima</persName>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>1 copy</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>
                        <persName>A S Myers</persName>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>1“</cell>
                    <cell>
                        <persName>J A Hart</persName>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>1“</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>
                        <persName>A Newark</persName>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>2“</cell>
                    <cell>
                        <persName>H Plahto</persName>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>1“</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>
                        <persName>J Kohn</persName>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>1“</cell>
                    <cell>
                        <persName role="author">H S Myers</persName>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>1“</cell>
                </row>
            </table>
            <p rend="indent(1)">10 copies in all</p>
            <p>let me know in your next if<lb/> you have commenced then the above<lb/> named persons
                are all of this city<lb/> I have <add>?</add> your circular<lb/> with my best wishes
                for your<lb/> welfare I subscribe</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">Myself yours Respectfully<add>?</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">
                <persName role="author">H Myers</persName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>Box 1515</placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="4"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
